sourcesContent: import React from "react" import Qualitie from "./qualitie" import BookMark from "./bookmark" import PropTypes from "prop-types" const User = ({ _id, name, qualities, profession, completedMeetings, rate, onDelete, bookmark, onToggleBookMark }) => { return ( {name} {qualities.map((qual) => ( ))} {profession.name} {completedMeetings} {rate} /5 onToggleBookMark(_id)} /> ) } User.propTypes = { _id: PropTypes.string.isRequired, name: PropTypes.string.isRequired, qualities: PropTypes.arrayOf(PropTypes.object), profession: PropTypes.objectOf(PropTypes.string), completedMeetings: PropTypes.number.isRequired, rate: PropTypes.number.isRequired, bookmark: PropTypes.bool.isRequired, onDelete: PropTypes.func.isRequired, onToggleBookMark: PropTypes.func.isRequired } export default User
